text:
Tenka, good work.
Um... are you okay...?

The steps were fast and difficult...
It was really... tough...

Even so, Tenka
you've been working hard until now.

Tenka, you've worked hard...
So... today is over...!

Hmm...
I really want to let you do that, but...

Tomorrow is your day off. So, to rest properly tomorrow,
could you keep going just a little bit longer?

B-But...
Oh, right... tomorrow is a day off...!

Okay then, Tenka...
Just a little bit more... Keep it up...

Yeah...! If I can't have a lesson tomorrow...
Then I have to do my best today...

Tenka...
That's the spirit for our unit live...

But... since tomorrow is a day off...
Will take lots of naps... and relax...!
